1
00:00:00,510 --> 00:00:01,810
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,810 --> 00:00:03,610
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,610 --> 00:00:05,140
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:07,010 --> 00:00:08,480
(Episode 46)

5
00:00:16,390 --> 00:00:17,390
It's me.

6
00:00:18,260 --> 00:00:20,660
I've got something we can use
to pressure Chairman Park.

7
00:00:22,560 --> 00:00:23,830
It's the truth about...

8
00:00:23,830 --> 00:00:25,730
what happened seven years ago
that he's been hiding.

9
00:00:27,570 --> 00:00:30,240
What truth?
What happened seven years ago?

10
00:00:30,600 --> 00:00:32,100
A secret that Park Min Jun,

11
00:00:32,370 --> 00:00:34,310
of all people, must never find out.

12
00:00:38,980 --> 00:00:40,980
I knew it. You did know something.

13
00:00:43,880 --> 00:00:44,880
Tell me.

14
00:00:45,520 --> 00:00:48,250
What happened seven years ago
that I'm not supposed to know about?

15
00:00:50,590 --> 00:00:52,060
Tell me right now.

16
00:00:56,430 --> 00:00:59,700
Hello?
Is Park Min Jun there with you?

17
00:01:00,470 --> 00:01:01,930
Don't say a word.

18
00:01:02,970 --> 00:01:04,670
Hello? Are you there?

19
00:01:08,570 --> 00:01:11,810
She's not about to tell Min Jun
about his father, is she?

20
00:01:16,350 --> 00:01:17,980
What happened back then?

21
00:01:18,620 --> 00:01:21,550
What's the secret
behind Jin Ju's accident seven years ago?

22
00:01:23,920 --> 00:01:24,920
Stop it.

23
00:01:25,490 --> 00:01:26,830
There's no secret.

24
00:01:26,890 --> 00:01:29,830
You said it yourself,
that there was a hidden truth.

25
00:01:30,830 --> 00:01:33,060
You were going to blackmail
my father with it.

26
00:01:33,060 --> 00:01:34,130
I was just...

27
00:01:36,170 --> 00:01:37,870
I didn't want to just give up,

28
00:01:38,470 --> 00:01:40,310
so I was looking for a way
to fight back.

29
00:01:40,910 --> 00:01:42,810
Are you going to keep lying?

30
00:01:46,110 --> 00:01:48,410
Fine. Forget it.

31
00:01:48,910 --> 00:01:51,120
I'll just ask my father myself.

32
00:01:52,550 --> 00:01:53,690
That's pointless!

33
00:01:57,520 --> 00:02:00,860
Do you have any idea
what kind of man your father is?

34
00:02:01,490 --> 00:02:03,630
He won't just tell you
because you ask.

35
00:02:04,930 --> 00:02:08,030
And even if you ask,
there's nothing for him to tell.

36
00:02:09,800 --> 00:02:11,970
Is the thought of me
meeting my father...

37
00:02:12,770 --> 00:02:14,270
making you uncomfortable?

38
00:02:15,610 --> 00:02:19,280
Do I have to play dumb
so you can blackmail him?

39
00:02:21,650 --> 00:02:25,220
I was just so frustrated
that I said I'd threaten him.

40
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:30,050
Please, don't make this
into something it's not.

41
00:02:30,990 --> 00:02:33,290
Fine. For now,

42
00:02:34,090 --> 00:02:35,460
we'll call it a misunderstanding.

43
00:02:48,270 --> 00:02:51,680
I have to act
before Min Jun ruins everything.

44
00:02:54,510 --> 00:02:56,550
I'll squeeze Chairman Park...

45
00:02:56,920 --> 00:03:00,180
for everything I can get
as fast as possible.

46
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:08,960
I've found out about your past.

47
00:03:09,830 --> 00:03:11,860
The past you tried to hide.

48
00:03:12,230 --> 00:03:14,500
The crime of murdering the daughter
of Munhwadang's chairman.

49
00:03:16,730 --> 00:03:17,740
Now,

50
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:20,000
you won't be able
to hide it anymore.

51
00:03:25,540 --> 00:03:26,540
Prove it.

52
00:03:27,310 --> 00:03:29,110
Do you have any proof I did it?

53
00:03:29,210 --> 00:03:30,320
Even if you did,

54
00:03:30,720 --> 00:03:33,790
what could you possibly do
about it now?

55
00:03:36,350 --> 00:03:37,360
True.

56
00:03:38,590 --> 00:03:40,260
It was so long ago...

57
00:03:40,260 --> 00:03:42,460
that the statute
of limitations has probably expired.

58
00:03:43,460 --> 00:03:44,730
Legally speaking,

59
00:03:45,530 --> 00:03:47,400
it might be difficult
to prosecute you.

60
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:49,830
But...

61
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:51,340
But what?

62
00:03:53,100 --> 00:03:57,410
What if the press finds out
that you're a murderer?

63
00:03:58,140 --> 00:04:00,450
Once details get out
that you took advantage of someone...

64
00:04:01,150 --> 00:04:02,950
with a heart condition...

65
00:04:03,410 --> 00:04:05,720
and used their own medication
against them,

66
00:04:05,880 --> 00:04:07,190
no matter where you go...

67
00:04:07,250 --> 00:04:08,850
or who you meet,

68
00:04:10,090 --> 00:04:12,090
people will see you as a killer,
won't they?

69
00:04:12,790 --> 00:04:15,630
Do you really think the shareholders
and the board of directors...

70
00:04:15,790 --> 00:04:19,330
will still side with you
and your son after that?

71
00:04:20,700 --> 00:04:22,900
You think I'm scared
of empty threats?

72
00:04:23,530 --> 00:04:27,070
The shareholders and the board?
Everyone can be bought with money.

73
00:04:27,210 --> 00:04:28,840
Then what about your son?

74
00:04:31,740 --> 00:04:36,180
What do you think will happen
when your son finds out the truth?

75
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:40,990
"You're the son of a murderer."

76
00:04:42,990 --> 00:04:44,920
How dare you bring my son into this?

77
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:49,390
You're threatening to torment my son
with rumors you can't even prove?

78
00:04:51,400 --> 00:04:53,900
You think I'll just stand by
and let that happen?

79
00:04:54,870 --> 00:04:56,330
If you so much as touch my son,

80
00:04:57,140 --> 00:04:59,000
I'll kill your son first.

81
00:05:00,770 --> 00:05:04,280
If the chairman finds out,
what do you think he'll do?

82
00:05:06,110 --> 00:05:08,080
If you so much as touch my Min Jun,

83
00:05:09,210 --> 00:05:10,310
do you think...

84
00:05:11,220 --> 00:05:13,180
you and your son will be safe?

85
00:05:14,950 --> 00:05:18,220
You... What's the point of this?

86
00:05:20,660 --> 00:05:25,600
It's my way of warning you
to stay out of my way.

87
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:31,000
I'm holding your secret,
your one true weakness.

88
00:05:31,670 --> 00:05:32,970
I can brand your son...

89
00:05:33,970 --> 00:05:38,010
as the son of a murderer.

90
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:40,880
You should never forget that.

91
00:05:42,450 --> 00:05:43,450
You...

92
00:05:44,250 --> 00:05:46,720
You crossed the line
when you involved my Hyun Jun.

93
00:05:47,890 --> 00:05:49,050
Mark my words.

94
00:05:49,950 --> 00:05:51,260
You're going to regret this.

95
00:06:08,370 --> 00:06:11,680
How on earth did she find out
about Munhwadang?

96
00:06:12,510 --> 00:06:14,650
I can't let her back me
into a corner like this.

97
00:06:31,030 --> 00:06:32,860
Is he looking down on me now too?

98
00:06:33,970 --> 00:06:37,970
Fine. I see that both mother
and son have a death wish.

99
00:06:42,140 --> 00:06:44,480
(Adele)

100
00:06:45,210 --> 00:06:47,410
Oh Jung Ran is inhuman.

101
00:06:47,410 --> 00:06:50,720
She killed her boss at Munhwadang
to take her place.

102
00:06:51,450 --> 00:06:54,550
And to keep the position she stole,
she went after Myung Hui.

103
00:06:55,590 --> 00:06:56,650
Now,

104
00:06:57,260 --> 00:06:59,720
I'm worried she'll come after you
and Min Jun too.

105
00:07:01,130 --> 00:07:03,830
That's why I still need Park Tae Ho.

106
00:07:04,660 --> 00:07:07,270
He's the only one Oh Jung Ran fears
more than the law.

107
00:07:07,730 --> 00:07:10,030
As long as Park Tae Ho
is protecting Min Jun,

108
00:07:10,670 --> 00:07:12,370
she won't dare lay a finger on him.

109
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:15,670
So? How did Oh Jung Ran take it?

110
00:07:16,270 --> 00:07:17,640
Do you think the threat
will work on her?

111
00:07:17,780 --> 00:07:20,040
She's not the type
to give in that easily.

112
00:07:20,710 --> 00:07:24,750
I'm going to show her exactly
how I'll play this card.

113
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:28,750
I'll start by forcing her
to give up the gallery.

114
00:07:29,620 --> 00:07:30,620
Good.

115
00:07:31,090 --> 00:07:34,530
It'll be quite a show when she loses
that gallery she treasures so much.

116
00:07:34,890 --> 00:07:38,130
First, the gallery.
Then the board of directors.

117
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:41,930
I'm going to strip away her power,
piece by piece.

118
00:07:44,340 --> 00:07:47,000
What? Choi Yu Na is being released?

119
00:07:47,840 --> 00:07:48,840
How?

120
00:07:48,910 --> 00:07:53,410
Chloe's new testimony altered
the estimated time of the accident.

121
00:07:53,910 --> 00:07:55,910
So she's been released
pending further investigation.

122
00:07:56,350 --> 00:07:57,650
Chloe.

123
00:07:59,520 --> 00:08:00,690
Just because the competition's over,

124
00:08:00,690 --> 00:08:02,890
has she already forgotten
that she was robbed?

125
00:08:03,960 --> 00:08:07,390
That misplaced sense of justice
is always the problem.

126
00:08:08,890 --> 00:08:10,830
What should we do about Choi Yu Na?

127
00:08:11,930 --> 00:08:14,030
Let's see what her next move is.

128
00:08:15,470 --> 00:08:16,770
I'm sure it won't be long...

129
00:08:18,100 --> 00:08:19,540
before she comes to us.

130
00:08:38,220 --> 00:08:39,220
You really came.

131
00:08:39,990 --> 00:08:44,200
I have a new card to play,
so why would I hesitate?

132
00:08:45,530 --> 00:08:49,630
When we spoke on the phone,
I thought I heard Park Min Jun.

133
00:08:50,300 --> 00:08:53,440
Does he know something too?

134
00:08:53,770 --> 00:08:54,770
No.

135
00:08:55,470 --> 00:08:59,940
I won't just show the card
I'll use against Chairman Park.

136
00:09:00,040 --> 00:09:03,680
What exactly do you have on him?

137
00:09:06,780 --> 00:09:09,150
We may be partners again,

138
00:09:10,290 --> 00:09:12,190
but do we really need
to share everything?

139
00:09:13,160 --> 00:09:17,430
I get what I want,
and you get the bio division.

140
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:20,330
All that matters is that
we both get what we want.

141
00:09:21,430 --> 00:09:22,500
I suppose.

142
00:09:23,370 --> 00:09:24,370
Fine.

143
00:09:28,310 --> 00:09:30,810
You'd better do a good job...

144
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:32,580
of blackmailing Chairman Park.

145
00:09:32,680 --> 00:09:33,780
Of course I will.

146
00:09:35,210 --> 00:09:37,750
He'll never dare
to treat me like that again.

147
00:09:53,730 --> 00:09:54,730
Right.

148
00:09:55,900 --> 00:09:59,640
I heard you were released
from police custody.

149
00:10:00,670 --> 00:10:03,470
Yes, I managed to escape
that little trap...

150
00:10:03,670 --> 00:10:05,040
you set for me.

151
00:10:05,680 --> 00:10:08,480
What... A trap?

152
00:10:09,350 --> 00:10:11,520
You're the one
who dug your own grave.

153
00:10:12,420 --> 00:10:14,250
Call it what you want.

154
00:10:15,690 --> 00:10:17,150
The point is, I'm back,

155
00:10:17,620 --> 00:10:19,690
and I'm going to get
exactly what I'm owed.

156
00:10:22,030 --> 00:10:23,030
What you're owed?

157
00:10:24,230 --> 00:10:25,930
It occurred to me...

158
00:10:26,700 --> 00:10:30,030
that I still have something on you.

159
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:32,400
Well...

160
00:10:33,400 --> 00:10:37,710
Are you saying you made a copy
of that recording?

161
00:10:38,510 --> 00:10:42,480
It's not exactly that,
but it'll have the same effect.

162
00:10:47,550 --> 00:10:49,190
The accident from seven years ago.

163
00:10:50,490 --> 00:10:52,920
If I tell President Kim Myung Hui
and Park Min Jun about it,

164
00:10:53,520 --> 00:10:54,730
what do you think will happen?

165
00:10:58,460 --> 00:11:01,530
Whatever nonsense you spout,
it'll be no use.

166
00:11:02,100 --> 00:11:06,700
I'll just say
you're a bitter woman lashing out...

167
00:11:07,740 --> 00:11:09,040
after losing everything.

168
00:11:09,610 --> 00:11:10,980
Are you sure about that?

169
00:11:11,710 --> 00:11:14,510
Even now,
Min Jun is still not over Jin Ju.

170
00:11:14,810 --> 00:11:18,620
So when he learns
that his own father killed her...

171
00:11:18,880 --> 00:11:21,250
- Choi Yu Na!
- Park Min Jun...

172
00:11:22,490 --> 00:11:25,260
will stop at nothing
to uncover the truth.

173
00:11:25,490 --> 00:11:27,530
If he actually finds out
what happened,

174
00:11:28,590 --> 00:11:30,190
will you be able to handle
the consequences?

175
00:11:33,430 --> 00:11:34,700
What about you?

176
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:37,000
You killed Baek Jin Ju, too.

177
00:11:38,070 --> 00:11:42,270
I still have the pen
with your confession on it.

178
00:11:42,340 --> 00:11:44,580
Then go ahead.
Release it to the world.

179
00:11:44,910 --> 00:11:48,010
I'll just keep screaming
that you made me do it.

180
00:11:49,380 --> 00:11:53,120
You'll have to be prepared
to cut ties with your son.

181
00:11:53,380 --> 00:11:54,420
In fact,

182
00:11:56,220 --> 00:11:59,220
you might have to kill Park Min Jun
with your own two hands...

183
00:11:59,420 --> 00:12:01,130
because he'll stop at nothing...

184
00:12:01,130 --> 00:12:03,230
to expose the truth
and make you pay.

185
00:12:05,230 --> 00:12:06,700
How dare you...

186
00:12:09,530 --> 00:12:11,570
If you don't want to destroy
your own son,

187
00:12:11,870 --> 00:12:14,110
put an end
to the police investigation.

188
00:12:14,110 --> 00:12:16,140
Then put everything back
the way it was,

189
00:12:16,540 --> 00:12:18,780
including my wedding and my job.

190
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:25,620
I'd get on that if I were you.

191
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:31,860
(Chairman Park Tae Ho)

192
00:12:39,230 --> 00:12:40,560
Choi Yu Na.

193
00:12:41,500 --> 00:12:43,400
I gave you one last chance,

194
00:12:44,500 --> 00:12:46,040
but you threw it back in my face?

195
00:12:50,310 --> 00:12:53,410
I knew it would work.

196
00:12:54,910 --> 00:12:57,850
I'm going to make the most
of the truth from seven years ago.

197
00:13:06,620 --> 00:13:08,490
The truth from seven years ago.

198
00:13:09,230 --> 00:13:11,960
So that was the leverage
Choi Yu Na had.

199
00:13:28,510 --> 00:13:29,650
It's a bit overdue,

200
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:32,550
but I want to apologize
for the other day.

201
00:13:35,720 --> 00:13:37,350
I'm also sorry about...

202
00:13:37,920 --> 00:13:38,920
what my mom did.

203
00:13:41,290 --> 00:13:43,030
Both back then and now,

204
00:13:43,460 --> 00:13:45,430
you're being completely one-sided,
even in your apology.

205
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:48,930
Fine, while I'm at it,

206
00:13:50,630 --> 00:13:52,270
I'll handle the wedding myself.

207
00:13:52,540 --> 00:13:54,410
- The wedding...
- I'd like to hurry things along.

208
00:13:54,740 --> 00:13:57,410
What should we do first?
Have our families meet?

209
00:13:57,940 --> 00:13:59,310
Or should we pick a date
and book the venue?

210
00:13:59,640 --> 00:14:02,310
- Look here.
- Why did you win the competition?

211
00:14:04,450 --> 00:14:05,950
Was it to beat Choi Yu Na?

212
00:14:06,520 --> 00:14:08,750
To break up Park Min Jun's wedding?

213
00:14:09,650 --> 00:14:11,260
Just so you won't get fired?

214
00:14:11,820 --> 00:14:12,820
I think...

215
00:14:13,690 --> 00:14:15,830
it was for the sake of our marriage.

216
00:14:18,530 --> 00:14:21,200
I'll start planning the wedding.

217
00:14:22,630 --> 00:14:23,970
You just follow my lead.

218
00:14:26,570 --> 00:14:29,710
(Bion Tech)

219
00:14:35,110 --> 00:14:36,610
Here are your drinks.

220
00:14:39,520 --> 00:14:40,520
Go ahead, Father.

221
00:14:45,560 --> 00:14:48,290
I should've come to you as soon
as marriage became a possibility.

222
00:14:48,990 --> 00:14:50,230
I'm sorry about that.

223
00:14:53,330 --> 00:14:55,000
You don't have to apologize...

224
00:14:55,300 --> 00:14:57,400
because I'm afraid
I have some bad news as well.

225
00:14:58,940 --> 00:14:59,970
Bad news?

226
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:04,510
I don't want Chloe to marry
into the Adele family.

227
00:15:04,780 --> 00:15:07,010
I've already told her
I'm against the wedding.

228
00:15:07,650 --> 00:15:11,020
And I trust that Chloe
will respect my wishes.

229
00:15:12,920 --> 00:15:14,950
So you've been against it all along.

230
00:15:16,250 --> 00:15:17,450
That must be why Chloe...

231
00:15:18,590 --> 00:15:20,220
hesitated about the wedding.

232
00:15:21,690 --> 00:15:23,530
I doubt I'm the only reason.

233
00:15:24,060 --> 00:15:27,160
I have a feeling there are others
who are against it.

234
00:15:28,270 --> 00:15:30,200
You don't have to worry
about my mother.

235
00:15:30,630 --> 00:15:34,310
Since my father approved,
she can't stay against it forever.

236
00:15:35,340 --> 00:15:37,240
What about Director Park Min Jun?

237
00:15:39,880 --> 00:15:43,350
What does he have to say
about your wedding?

238
00:15:47,250 --> 00:15:48,250
I couldn't say.

239
00:15:48,850 --> 00:15:52,320
I see no reason why Park Min Jun
would get involved in our wedding.

240
00:15:54,260 --> 00:15:55,590
In any case,

241
00:15:56,160 --> 00:15:57,930
I have made my position clear.

242
00:16:01,570 --> 00:16:02,570
Then I suppose...

243
00:16:03,370 --> 00:16:05,200
I'll make my position clear as well.

244
00:16:09,340 --> 00:16:12,410
I won't give up on this marriage.

245
00:16:16,180 --> 00:16:18,980
I'm not the type to be swayed
by what others think.

246
00:16:19,980 --> 00:16:21,490
I've made my decision,

247
00:16:21,490 --> 00:16:22,990
and since
there's no reason to call it off,

248
00:16:24,420 --> 00:16:25,690
I'm moving forward with it.

249
00:16:37,270 --> 00:16:39,540
This is about to get
a lot more complicated.

250
00:16:45,110 --> 00:16:46,910
She knows about Munhwadang?

251
00:16:47,710 --> 00:16:49,080
President Kim knows?

252
00:16:49,680 --> 00:16:52,420
- How?
- How should I know?

253
00:16:53,720 --> 00:16:54,790
Could someone...

254
00:16:55,390 --> 00:16:57,650
have told her
about the rumors back then?

255
00:16:58,390 --> 00:17:00,820
After the daughter
of Munhwadang's owner died,

256
00:17:00,890 --> 00:17:05,160
there were whispers everywhere
that you took her place.

257
00:17:05,230 --> 00:17:06,560
I don't think it's just that.

258
00:17:07,330 --> 00:17:09,630
She knew the exact drug I used.

259
00:17:10,200 --> 00:17:11,200
The drug, too?

260
00:17:11,340 --> 00:17:14,340
On top of that,
she's using Hyun Jun to threaten me.

261
00:17:14,340 --> 00:17:15,340
What?

262
00:17:15,770 --> 00:17:17,640
Why bring Hyun Jun into this?

263
00:17:18,780 --> 00:17:22,180
She's threatening to tell Hyun Jun
everything from back then...

264
00:17:22,180 --> 00:17:23,810
No, she can't do that.

265
00:17:25,280 --> 00:17:28,390
He has such a tender heart.
It would crush him.

266
00:17:28,520 --> 00:17:29,890
Exactly.

267
00:17:30,320 --> 00:17:32,920
That Kim Myung Hui
is going completely berserk.

268
00:17:32,990 --> 00:17:35,160
Then you have to stop her.

269
00:17:35,230 --> 00:17:37,960
She must want something, right?

270
00:17:38,260 --> 00:17:39,860
Offer her whatever she wants,

271
00:17:39,930 --> 00:17:43,270
and as long as she doesn't
say a word to Hyun Jun...

272
00:17:43,730 --> 00:17:46,770
No, wait. Just beg her, please.

273
00:17:46,940 --> 00:17:47,940
Are you crazy?

274
00:17:47,940 --> 00:17:50,670
We're desperate enough to do that!

275
00:17:51,070 --> 00:17:52,080
Forget it.

276
00:17:52,980 --> 00:17:57,380
If she lays a finger on my son,
I'll do the exact same thing to her.

277
00:17:57,880 --> 00:17:59,320
What do you have in mind?

278
00:18:09,590 --> 00:18:10,590
That reminds me.

279
00:18:11,330 --> 00:18:13,830
I have something to report, sir.

280
00:18:15,100 --> 00:18:16,100
What is it?

281
00:18:17,430 --> 00:18:21,970
Your wife said she's leaving
all the gallery work to me.

282
00:18:23,470 --> 00:18:24,480
All of it?

283
00:18:26,640 --> 00:18:29,280
What? No, that's not it.

284
00:18:29,280 --> 00:18:31,480
Ms. Oh said...

285
00:18:31,850 --> 00:18:34,250
she was taking a short break
from the gallery.

286
00:18:34,650 --> 00:18:38,290
She needs to focus
on Hyun Jun's wedding from now on.

287
00:18:39,020 --> 00:18:40,020
Isn't that right?

288
00:18:41,730 --> 00:18:42,730
Is that true?

289
00:18:53,800 --> 00:18:57,370
Mom said she would accept Chloe.
Now she's helping with the wedding.

290
00:18:57,810 --> 00:19:00,880
If it's not urgent,
please let Mom do as she pleases.

291
00:19:01,180 --> 00:19:04,010
I'm planning to move the wedding up,
so I could really use the help.

292
00:19:05,120 --> 00:19:06,120
That's Ms. Oh for you.

293
00:19:06,120 --> 00:19:08,050
Once she's decided,
she follows through.

294
00:19:10,990 --> 00:19:12,460
Are you kidding me?

295
00:19:13,090 --> 00:19:15,390
Do you really think
I'll let you have your way?

296
00:19:17,490 --> 00:19:20,000
Honey, it's not like that.

297
00:19:21,700 --> 00:19:22,800
(Mioxin)

298
00:19:26,640 --> 00:19:28,010
What...

299
00:19:28,910 --> 00:19:31,380
Why do you have this?

300
00:19:32,780 --> 00:19:35,510
I saw this pill bottle
while I was cleaning the annex.

301
00:19:35,810 --> 00:19:38,980
I thought it might be yours,
so I brought it with me.

302
00:19:45,860 --> 00:19:48,030
Ms. Oh, are you on medication?

303
00:19:49,060 --> 00:19:51,230
Why? What's it for?

304
00:19:51,800 --> 00:19:52,800
Don't!

305
00:19:55,930 --> 00:19:58,240
Kim Myung Hui is right
about everything.

306
00:19:58,600 --> 00:20:01,140
I'll step away from the gallery
and take a break.

307
00:20:01,740 --> 00:20:05,310
Let her handle it
and see how well she does.

308
00:20:13,050 --> 00:20:16,490
Did something happen
between you two?

309
00:20:18,160 --> 00:20:19,160
Of course not.

310
00:20:19,760 --> 00:20:22,190
Ms. Oh is just very busy...

311
00:20:23,090 --> 00:20:24,560
and has a lot on her mind.

312
00:20:25,900 --> 00:20:28,670
She hasn't even been able to focus
on the tasks you assigned,

313
00:20:29,270 --> 00:20:32,470
and you know she's falling behind
on selling those paintings.

314
00:20:34,500 --> 00:20:35,570
I suppose so, but...

315
00:20:36,670 --> 00:20:39,210
She's probably just stressed
about my wedding.

316
00:20:39,680 --> 00:20:40,940
Please let her take a break
for a while.

317
00:20:41,950 --> 00:20:45,320
Then I'll assume
I have your permission as well.

318
00:20:48,220 --> 00:20:49,220
Fine.

319
00:20:50,220 --> 00:20:52,020
Go ahead and give it a shot.

320
00:21:11,040 --> 00:21:12,140
Kim Myung Hui.

321
00:21:12,780 --> 00:21:15,510
How dare you drag my son
into this...

322
00:21:16,280 --> 00:21:17,850
and steal the gallery from me?

323
00:21:20,180 --> 00:21:21,180
Just you wait.

324
00:21:21,790 --> 00:21:24,690
I'm going to take away
what's most precious to you too.

325
00:21:37,130 --> 00:21:39,240
Do you need anything?

326
00:21:39,970 --> 00:21:41,000
I was wondering...

327
00:21:42,270 --> 00:21:43,270
Yes?

328
00:21:44,040 --> 00:21:45,640
The medicine bottle from earlier.

329
00:21:46,510 --> 00:21:48,710
Why did you bring it back
instead of throwing it away?

330
00:21:49,910 --> 00:21:52,450
There were still a lot of pills left
in the bottle.

331
00:21:52,750 --> 00:21:55,850
I thought she dropped it by mistake,
not that she threw it away,

332
00:21:55,850 --> 00:21:56,850
so I picked it up.

333
00:21:57,450 --> 00:22:00,290
Why? Is something wrong?

334
00:22:01,390 --> 00:22:03,490
No, I was just curious.

335
00:22:04,030 --> 00:22:05,130
I'll leave you to it, then.

336
00:22:06,000 --> 00:22:07,000
Yes, ma'am.

337
00:22:22,710 --> 00:22:25,780
The accident from seven years ago.
Choi Yu Na...

338
00:22:27,950 --> 00:22:29,050
and my father.

339
00:22:30,050 --> 00:22:32,360
It seems Chairman Park
was involved too.

340
00:22:34,320 --> 00:22:35,560
Am I right?

341
00:22:37,890 --> 00:22:40,000
I'm sorry,
but I can't tell you anything.

342
00:22:42,130 --> 00:22:43,600
You're not denying it.

343
00:22:53,640 --> 00:22:55,610
What did my father do?

344
00:22:56,310 --> 00:22:59,450
Was the car accident
from seven years ago...

345
00:23:00,820 --> 00:23:02,450
actually an accident?

346
00:23:10,930 --> 00:23:12,660
That's for you to figure out
on your own.

347
00:23:14,430 --> 00:23:15,430
I'm sorry.

348
00:23:16,870 --> 00:23:17,900
I'll be leaving now.

349
00:24:00,940 --> 00:24:04,150
Park Min Jun, of all people,
wanted to see me.

350
00:24:05,680 --> 00:24:08,290
Do you know this is the first time
you've ever invited me out?

351
00:24:10,250 --> 00:24:11,250
Really?

352
00:24:13,490 --> 00:24:16,790
Is this really our first time
spending time like this?

353
00:24:43,390 --> 00:24:44,390
Jin Ju.

354
00:24:45,190 --> 00:24:48,660
Park Min Jun is suspicious
of Chairman Park.

355
00:24:49,590 --> 00:24:52,760
Looks like he's meeting Choi Yu Na
to try and confirm it.

356
00:24:53,730 --> 00:24:55,000
How did this happen all of a sudden?

357
00:24:56,970 --> 00:24:58,540
Do you have any idea
what's going on?

358
00:24:59,440 --> 00:25:01,870
Choi Yu Na slipped up
in front of Min Jun.

359
00:25:02,410 --> 00:25:04,140
So now it looks like
he's trying to dig deeper.

360
00:25:06,680 --> 00:25:08,410
Are you sure it's okay
to just stand by and watch?

361
00:25:09,010 --> 00:25:11,650
Choi Yu Na won't talk so easily.

362
00:25:12,620 --> 00:25:15,750
It's the only leverage she has
against Chairman Park.

363
00:25:18,420 --> 00:25:19,420
Still,

364
00:25:20,460 --> 00:25:22,290
I think I should check
on the situation.

365
00:25:22,730 --> 00:25:24,090
I'm heading over there now.

366
00:25:25,460 --> 00:25:27,060
Okay, got it.

367
00:25:33,940 --> 00:25:35,870
(Park Min Jun,
Adele's Head of Division 1)

368
00:25:35,940 --> 00:25:37,870
As long as Choi Yu Na
doesn't slip up, we're fine.

369
00:25:39,640 --> 00:25:41,210
Even if he becomes suspicious
of Chairman Park,

370
00:25:42,610 --> 00:25:43,680
that's all it'll be.

371
00:25:46,120 --> 00:25:47,480
It can all stop right there.

372
00:25:54,760 --> 00:25:55,890
Here.

373
00:25:57,260 --> 00:25:59,430
This is our first time
drinking together.

374
00:26:12,880 --> 00:26:14,780
If this is about last time...

375
00:26:15,480 --> 00:26:17,050
and you're fishing for information,

376
00:26:18,010 --> 00:26:19,020
forget it.

377
00:26:19,450 --> 00:26:22,350
I'm not going to tell you anything,
no matter how drunk I get.

378
00:26:23,790 --> 00:26:25,190
Nothing to tell me?

379
00:26:26,260 --> 00:26:29,460
Fine. Then have a drink and leave.

380
00:26:59,790 --> 00:27:00,790
Seriously?

381
00:27:01,520 --> 00:27:03,890
Didn't you call me here to dig into
what happened seven years ago?

382
00:27:05,030 --> 00:27:08,230
Why did you just drink by yourself
and get totally wasted?

383
00:27:12,270 --> 00:27:14,700
What were you even thinking,
calling me here?

384
00:27:25,420 --> 00:27:26,420
Park Min Jun.

385
00:27:28,150 --> 00:27:29,520
I never knew
you had this side to you.

386
00:27:32,090 --> 00:27:34,020
You were always distant with me...

387
00:27:34,890 --> 00:27:36,360
and quick to get angry.

388
00:27:47,570 --> 00:27:48,710
What you're feeling...

389
00:27:49,340 --> 00:27:50,670
isn't love.

390
00:27:50,670 --> 00:27:53,410
It's just greed and selfishness.

391
00:27:55,480 --> 00:27:56,550
Greed?

392
00:27:59,420 --> 00:28:00,720
You may not know this,

393
00:28:01,620 --> 00:28:03,120
but I have every right to be greedy.

394
00:28:04,190 --> 00:28:05,190
Because...

395
00:28:06,220 --> 00:28:07,860
having you is my compensation...

396
00:28:09,330 --> 00:28:10,530
for what I did that day.

397
00:28:12,860 --> 00:28:14,260
Yu Na!

398
00:28:33,020 --> 00:28:34,250
So I can live without regrets...

399
00:28:35,650 --> 00:28:37,550
and stand by my decision,

400
00:28:40,420 --> 00:28:42,260
I'm going to have you,
no matter what.

401
00:28:49,670 --> 00:28:50,870
I want you.

402
00:29:54,100 --> 00:29:55,330
Jin Ju.

403
00:29:56,930 --> 00:29:58,130
Baek Jin Ju.

404
00:30:00,840 --> 00:30:01,910
Baek Jin Ju?

405
00:30:03,370 --> 00:30:04,810
Even at a time like this...

406
00:30:26,360 --> 00:30:27,400
Jin Ju.

407
00:30:28,930 --> 00:30:30,400
I swear...

408
00:30:31,800 --> 00:30:33,140
I'll get revenge for you.

409
00:30:37,540 --> 00:30:38,540
Revenge?

410
00:30:40,310 --> 00:30:42,110
The car accident seven years ago.

411
00:30:43,580 --> 00:30:45,320
It wasn't just an accident, was it?

412
00:30:47,050 --> 00:30:48,420
Choi Yu Na killed you...

413
00:30:50,020 --> 00:30:51,050
on purpose, didn't she?

414
00:30:52,860 --> 00:30:53,860
What?

415
00:30:58,260 --> 00:30:59,800
For you,

416
00:31:00,430 --> 00:31:01,660
I'll make them all pay.

417
00:31:02,370 --> 00:31:04,130
I'll make them pay...

418
00:31:05,100 --> 00:31:06,240
for killing you, Jin Ju.

419
00:31:09,710 --> 00:31:11,270
Me? Why?

420
00:31:13,010 --> 00:31:15,140
Jin Ju, I'll make them suffer
1,000 times more...

421
00:31:15,610 --> 00:31:17,180
than you ever suffered.

422
00:31:19,750 --> 00:31:23,790
- I...
- I'll make it worse than death!

423
00:31:27,290 --> 00:31:28,290
No!

424
00:31:34,960 --> 00:31:36,470
I had no other choice.

425
00:31:39,900 --> 00:31:41,270
You don't know anything.

426
00:31:42,870 --> 00:31:43,870
You should just...

427
00:31:44,710 --> 00:31:47,110
stay out of it and do nothing.

428
00:31:49,150 --> 00:31:51,050
You can never get revenge for her,

429
00:31:52,550 --> 00:31:53,980
and you'll never win.

430
00:32:03,190 --> 00:32:04,530
You had no choice?

431
00:32:05,630 --> 00:32:07,330
You're saying it wasn't an accident,

432
00:32:08,770 --> 00:32:10,230
but you had no choice?

433
00:32:45,500 --> 00:32:48,540
(Pearl in Red)

434
00:32:48,770 --> 00:32:50,140
I'm afraid...

435
00:32:50,610 --> 00:32:54,240
he'll do something stupid and reckless
for my sake.

436
00:32:54,380 --> 00:32:56,480
Right, I still have a chance.

437
00:32:56,550 --> 00:32:57,980
I have to silence Min Jun.

438
00:32:58,050 --> 00:32:59,980
To get something out
of Chairman Park quickly...

439
00:33:01,150 --> 00:33:03,920
But how? How do I silence Min Jun?

440
00:33:04,020 --> 00:33:08,790
Chairman Park,
I no longer wish to be your son.

441
00:33:08,830 --> 00:33:11,230
I'm leaving the company
and this family behind.

442
00:33:11,230 --> 00:33:14,900
Right here, right now,
I'm cutting all ties.

443
00:33:14,900 --> 00:33:15,930
Min Jun, wait.

444
00:33:16,070 --> 00:33:18,070
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
